<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd">
<concept id="concept_a2n_3fk_5v">
 <title>Upgrade</title>
 <shortdesc>You can upgrade a previous version of <ph
            conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/> to a
        new version. You can upgrade an installation from the tarball, an installation from the RPM
        package, or an installation with Cloudera Manager.</shortdesc>
    <conbody>
        <note type="important">The minimum requirements for <ph
                conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/>
            can change with each version. Before you upgrade to a new version, verify that the
            machine meets the latest minimum requirements as described in <xref
                href="../Install_Config/Requirements.dita#concept_vzg_n2p_kq"/>.</note>
    </conbody>
</concept>
